[{"Id": 1002832, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "As quoted from Makarim al-Akhlaq. If you have an urgent request to be granted by Almighty Allah due to which your heart is distressed, you may offer a 2 rakat namaz. Upon accomplishment, you may repeat the Takbir statement (ie. Allahu Akbar) 3 times and then utter the Tasbeeh’e Zahra (s). Then you may prostrate yourself and repeat the following statement 100 times…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Makarimul Akhlaq mein riwaayat hai keh jab tumhe koi haajat dar-pesh ho aur us se tumhara dil ghabra raha ho, to 2 rakat namaz adaa karo Namaz ke baad 3 martaba “Allahu Akbar” kahe aur phir Tasbeeh’e Zahra (s) ke baad sajdeh mein ja kar 100 martaba is zikr ko dauraaye…", "UrduDescription": "ایک روایت میں ہے : جب تمہیں کوئی حاجت در پیش ہو اور اس سے تمہار ا دل گھبرا رہا ہو تو ۲ رکعت نماز ادا کرو تشہد و سلام کے بعد۳ مرتبہ اللہ اکبر کہو،تسبیح حضرت زہرا ؑ پڑھو اور پھر سجدے میں سر رکھ کر ۱۰۰ مرتبہ کہو۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9":