": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "You may then put your right cheek on the ground and repeat the same 100 times, put your left cheek on the ground and repeat the same 100 times, and return to the normal position of prostration and repeat the same 110 times. You may then submit your requests, inshallah will be granted.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Iske baad apna daayna rukhsaar (right cheek) zameen par rakkhe aur wohi zikr ko 100 martaba kahe phir baaya’n rukhsaar (left cheek) zameen par rakkhe aur usi zikr ko 100 martaba dauraaye. Phir sar sajdeh mein rakh kar 110 martaba wohi dauraaye. Ab apni haajaat bayaan kare, inshallah qabool hogi.", "UrduDescription": "پھر اپنا دایاں رخسارزمین پر رکھ کر ۱۰۰ مرتبہ یہی کہو،اس کے بعد اپنا بایاں رخسار زمین پر رکھ کر ۱۰۰ مرتبہ یہی کہو پھر سر سجدے میں رکھ کر ۱۱۰ مرتبہ یہی کہو اس کے بعد اپنی حاجات بیان کرو،یقینًا خدا وند عالم یہ دعائیں ضرور قبول فرمائے گا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null,